Class RSSQuantiles

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.streaminer.stream.quantile.rss.RSSQuantiles
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IQuantiles<Double>

    public class RSSQuantiles
extends Object
implements IQuantiles<Double>, Serializable
    A stream version of the rss technique presented by Anna Gilbert, Yannis Kotidis, S. Muthukrishanan, and Matrin Strauss in the paper "How to summarize the Universe".
    Author:
    Carsten Przyluczky
